      **  MEMBER :  XSDU0005                                         **
      **  REMARKS:  MIXED CASE SUPPORT.                              **
      **            THIS MODULE PERFORMS MIXED TO UPPER-CASE         **
      **            CONVERSIONS. BASED ON THE REQUEST, IT WILL       **
      **            CONVERT THE LOWER CASE CHARACTERS TO UPPER CASE  **
      **            WITH OR WITHOUT ACCENTS.                         **
      **  DOMAIN :  SY                                               **
      *****************************************************************
      **  DATE     AUTH.  DESCRIPTION                                **
      **                                                             **
